Re: My shot at a translation (corrections please)
by Hyperworm » Tue 02.16.2010 4:14 pm As of 2009-06-15, the license has been updated, such that the text of the Japanese version of Wikipedia, and some of its files, are now usable under the "Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike License" in addition to the "GNU Free Documentation License".I think fun translation snippets | need something translated?BTC@1KMZXgoWiDshQis5Z7feCx8jaiP4QAB2ks
